.TH LOA-MAN 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
man \- Show bundled command manual pages from inside alexandria
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> man add
.br
alexandria> man reading add
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Requires an exact command name.
.TP
Opens the matching bundled page (for example \fBloa-add.1\fR).
.TP
If the system \fBman\fR command is available, pages are rendered normally.
.TP
If \fBman\fR is unavailable, a plain text fallback is shown.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> man progress
.TP
alexandria> man reading remove
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1)
.SH AUTHOR
Generated for the Library Of Alexandria project.
